Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though they're called draking vessels,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not like we're fighting dragons\Nevery day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's the everyday work\Nwhich is the hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Jiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Takita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Time to switch?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on laundry duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm good at doing laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Up we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she gonna be alright...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How rare for you to have\Na hangover, Vanabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, honey and ginger juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had a drink before sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mixed drink...\NCheap alcohol's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshi-san, do you have any laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then take that towel, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Vannie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you when I finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.95,0:01:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! Please rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Any laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, shut up for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a fight between men.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to give up, you better\Ndo it before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!! Why!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight between men...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Soraya, you're terrible with bets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth, Faye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You better pay me\Nwhen you get your next wage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Takita, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pour some water on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that shampoo? Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice how it's been\Npretty calm lately, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's when it gets busy,\Nso get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it gonna be that hectic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it will be like shooting fish\Nin a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't possibly miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um? When was the last time\NI washed my hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Want me to lend you some washing powder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of hair\Nand it's troublesome to wash so I kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes... you never know\Nwhat you've got till it's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're actually concerned about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what is it, Mika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do... do I stink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot of trouble, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a fun... workplace... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,29%.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,29 per cent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I can't believe you can guess\Nthe position of the ship so high in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for me,\NI don't understand a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro-san, you're so skillful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone on a ship should be able\Nto do this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you follow the process in order,\Nanyone can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's just too sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs-san said it though!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That your observations are\Nthe most accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who teached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad... was a draker too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Now I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad must have been outstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was really irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Casually coming home, and then\Ngoing out again just as casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving me and my mom alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When he came home,\Nhe only talked about dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been not a single sign of them\Nfor the past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,With this weather, we can't expect much either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, if we continue like this,\Nwe'll be deep in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't have been like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Crocco?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... we also need to refuel already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go across the sea towards northwest\Nand find some land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Gibbs-san, here.\N-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco-san, I think a storm is\Napproaching after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The pressure on the mercury column is dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab the guys that are off-duty today\Nand go check if the cargo is properly secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro-san, how did you know\Na storm is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the wind feels a bit lukewarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you can know\Nbecause of the smell, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell something... burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! A fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoking meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire was too strong and it\Nmade too much smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we had some old salted meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the red meat, and below that, fat meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're using grappa from an oak barrel\Nso it'll smell really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, with every little adjustment\Nthe flavor can change in unexpected ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoking is pretty deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop looking at it...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You're going too, Mika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I gotta watch over the smoked meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like you can do anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-S... stop I tell you!\N-Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you just wanted to snitch food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go. You help too, Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pile it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it down and fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The clouds are starting to look pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe today is the day we finally see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, tell her about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of the glittering dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Glittering dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the glittering dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, a ship ran across a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, what happened to that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the storm just got stronger\Nand stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone aboard came to terms\Nwith the fact that they were done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Obstructed by thunderclouds,\Nand with their compass broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,they couldn't tell south from north.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But in that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,between the clouds, they could see a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone said
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"This light comes from a town!\NWe'll be saved!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But something was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That light was slowly approaching\Nthe ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what appeared before the crew members\Nholding their breath was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A glittering dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if the ship was bewitched,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was drawn in to that dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows how much time passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but when they noticed, they had left\Nthe storm behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The glittering dragon saved them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the drakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there are a few of those superstitions\Ngoing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, before Jiro came to this ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,he believed his dad's stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That happened a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always bringing up things\Nfrom when I was a newbie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're on a ship, there's nothing\Nbut troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure wish a dragon saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If a dragon like that exists,\NI'd love to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it maybe does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, no one has ever seen\Nall the dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ate a glittering dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think my stomach would shine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,From the inside, like bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell if I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, I don't see you working!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind has gotten quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we change the course?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The clouds are growing too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The storm already caught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... everyone listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather has gotten rough!\NThe storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko and Oken who are on duty,\Nto the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Faye and Soraya go help the engine room,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone else stand by on your cabins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else, follow Gibbs' orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You two check over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If it stops now, it'll fall apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're always so reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we had a more... safe sail...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Move your hands!\N-Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, put your safety belts on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Also, Capella!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the toilet while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, you don't need to\Nkeep watch anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down here before you get blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the clouds better here\Nthan in the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't predict the flow of the clouds,\Nwe won't be able to get out of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay and keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, you have great eyes,\Nwe're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch with me. I'll be on the front,\Nyou behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoked salty salo, freshly made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not in a picnic, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep watch with\Nan empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let the clouds at the front distract you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A wall of clouds at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes all the way to the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, do you think we can\Npass through that side?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go over the clouds at 9 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,30 to port!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go above the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise the tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This goddamn storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The rudder feels so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Engine room! We're increasing the output!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ahh, come on!\N-Check over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The clouds on the front were hiding it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the ship stand in the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't! We're being swept away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we continue like this we won't\Nbe able to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, don't let it shake you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been surrounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't lift it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we cut through the clouds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vortex of air currents!\NWe'd be torn to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The only option is to slip between the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right...\N-For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So close...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get away from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I stink?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mika-san and Jiro-san are okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope Jiro doesn't do anything reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, how's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So far so good, keep going straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't change the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's electrified?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance we'll probably never have again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,being able to fly in the middle of this storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The thunderclouds will bring us the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's going to appear,\Nit has to be under this sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, let me sit at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Being at the front all the time\Nwears you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know when will we able to\Nget out of this storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That light was slowly approaching\Nthe ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And what appeared before the crew members\Nholding their breath was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A glittering dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, look towards port!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Capture it!\N-The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you insane?!\NWe're in the middle of a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you plan to capture it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We better do it quick or it'll get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just listen to me and\Nbring the ship closer!\N-As if I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That dragon will show us the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we follow it, we should be able\Nto get out of the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, are you for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If the dragon is flying\Navoiding the thunderclouds
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun, I think we should trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we capture that dragon, we'd be rolling in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! If it's not one it's the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, I leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh- hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika... were you really planning on\Ncatching it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We were lucky we got to slip out\Nof the storm at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I let such a big prey\Nescape from under my own nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, let the legend be a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Legends won't fill your stomach, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, the food is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What do we have today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no meat in here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is though,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't call this meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens when we don't\Ncatch dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much food left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna complain\NI'm taking it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
